description:
Lovely fun platforming game where u deliver a cake 2 your best friend in the world… watch out for the lava rising “EVERY 10 SECONDS”!!!

controlz:

z/up/“a button”: jump!!

l-stick/arrow keys: move!!

r/“y button”: die/reset level

f4: fullscreen

n: next level (cheater….)

esc: quit to operating system

soundtrack (stream + DL)
